issue.title: Product List Loading Screen Issues: Blaze Banner is visible
issue.body: The loading screen of the product list seems to be broken because: - The blaze banner is shown in background. - It's possible to tap the actions in the Blaze banner, like "Try Blaze now". - At the same time, It's possible to see the loading cells. - I entered in a state where other screens (like Orders) load correctly, here it's impossible to go out of this loading state. Not easy to replicate. Version 14.8 beta.
